Atok raises par value to one peso per share . Mining firm Atok Big Wedge Co said on Tuesday its board had approved a plan to increase the par value of its shares to one peso each from the present one centavo . Atok shares have been on the upsurge since the start of the year . It had risen to 4 . 8 pesos by midsession on Tuesday from a just 41 centavos on January 2 . Brokers said the stock had surged on speculation it was planning to convert to a holding firm . In the past few months , several dormant Manila firms have turned into holding companies and ventured into the booming property business . - Manila newsroom 63 2 8418938 Fax 8176267 
